descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset was created for diploma (master's) thesis about transfer learning with data augmentation.


### Content

There are 6 types (classes) of coins - 1 CZK, 2 CZK, 5 CZK, 10 CZK, 20 CZK and 50 CZK. Coins were captured from both sides, on different surfaces, under different lighting conditions and from different angles. Each class consists of roughly 300 images (~1800 images total), image size is 640x640px.

*NOTE: [10 CZK - 2000 version](https://www.cnb.cz/en/banknotes-and-coins/coins/10-czk-2000-version/), [20 CZK - 2000 version](https://www.cnb.cz/en/banknotes-and-coins/coins/20-czk-2000-version/), [20 CZK - 2018 version](https://www.cnb.cz/en/banknotes-and-coins/coins/20-czk-2018-i-version/), [20 CZK - 2019 version](https://www.cnb.cz/en/banknotes-and-coins/coins/20-czk-2019-i-version/) are not present in this dataset.*

subtitle: Small image dataset for classification
